# Level: Kithgard Dungeon
# Goal: Defeat the ogres and grab the gem.

# The code here is just a simple example of the kind of code used in CodeCombat levels.

# Move towards the enemy.
hero.moveRight()

# Attack the enemy.
hero.attack('Krogg')

# Keep moving towards the gem.
hero.moveRight()
hero.moveDown()

# Grab the gem.
hero.moveRight()

# Move towards the exit.
hero.moveRight()
hero.moveUp()
hero.moveRight()
